<H3> <TI>   Daily on Summit, Attitudes to EU </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Daily on Summit, Attitudes to EU </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU0706121294 Munich SUEDDEUTSCHE ZEITUNG in German 7 Jun 94 
p 4 </F>

<F P=103> AU0706121294 </F>
<F P=104>  Munich SUEDDEUTSCHE ZEITUNG </F>
<F P=105>  German </F>


