Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary to Greece Arman 
Kirakosyan to high-ranking Greek officials. The ambassador will 
present his credentials to President Konstandinos Karamanlis. 
Vahan Papazyan will leave for Istanbul on 9 June to take part 
in the regular NATO Cooperation Council foreign ministers 
conference. 

