<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Increased Whaling Quota Condemned by UK </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM0806120494 London THE DAILY TELEGRAPH in English 8 Jun 94 
p 13 </F>

<F P=103> PM0806120494 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE DAILY TELEGRAPH </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


