BFN 

  [Text] Turkish Cypriot leader Rauf Denktas today clarified 
the Turkish Cypriot side's positions on the confidence-building 
measures, as they were expressed on 6 May. Denktas made the 
clarification in a meeting this afternoon with Gustave Feissel, 
