<H3> <TI>   Commissioner Urges Italy To Continue Austerity Policy </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Commissioner Urges Italy To Continue Austerity Policy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2605133794 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 1617 GMT 25 
May 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR2605133794 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
