free trade zone" because of enlargement. "This was not the 
intention of the founders. This is not our intention," 
Mitterrand said. "For me enlargement and deepening is no 
contradiction," Kohl stressed. 
  The chancellor stated that Mitterrand's announcement that he 
will invite the Eurocorps and those politically responsible in 
the participating countries for the military parade on 14 July, 
the French National Day, is a "wonderful gesture." 

